title: Let's quote roles and their common blame game :^)
body:
Jungler: "Not my job to win your lane"

ADC: "Noob support never peels"

Top *(While pushed to enemy turret)* : "Fucking jungler never ganks and this Lee has been top 5 times in the past 4 minutes"

Mid: "Wouldn't have died if I had A FUCKING BLUE BUFF"

#More pls
